ata loss due to device malfunction\n- network, connection or P2P infrastructure issues\n- damages caused by illegal behavior of other users\n\n7. Acceptance of terms\nTo use the app, the user must read this document in full, accept the terms and conditions, and confirm their responsibility in using the app. If the user does not accept, they cannot use WinkWink.",

